Title: A-Gas Large Rental Receiver Cylinder 45kg
Description: This A-Gas large 45kg recovery cylinder with yellow and black banded valve guard is designed to be used temporary storage for refrigerant that will be re-introduced into a system. The cylinder includes a dual port valve for straightforward push-pull recovery of gas.
category: Refrigeration/Refrigeration Cylinders/Receiver Cylinders/Receiver Cylinders.csv -> A-Gas Large Rental Receiver Cylinder 45kg
Feature 2: Dual port valves enable push-pull gas recovery
Feature 4: Different refrigerants should not be mixed
Feature 5: Maximum fill weight stencilled and labelled on cylinder
Feature 6: Maximum fill weight should be adhered to at all times
Feature 7: Standard recovery cylinder not suitable for hydrocarbons and high pressure refrigerants

Title: A-Gas rental flammable receiver 10kg
Description: This A-Gas 10kg flammable receiver cylinder with yellow and black banded valve guard is designed to be used temporary storage for refrigerant that will be re-introduced into a system. It is designed to handle flammable hydrocarbon refrigerants.
